  "anger... jealousy... fear"          | 3 images    | anger / jealousy / fear
  "destroy life OR turn into leader"   | 2 images    | destroy life / become leader
  "enemies into allies"                | 1 image     | enemies → allies (transition)
  "failure into absolute mastery"      | 1 image     | failure → mastery (contrast)
  "inhale... hold... exhale"           | 3 images    | inhale / hold / exhale
  "People will provoke you"            | 1 image     | provocation scene
  "People will try to belittle you"    | 1 image     | belittling scene
  "every time breathe... you win"      | 1 image     | win scene
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  RULES:
  - Each sub-beat = its own distinct situation — not the same image repeated
  - Do NOT split mechanically every 2 seconds — split based on MEANING
  - Each split must have a DIFFERENT visual situation in mind
  - Plan ALL ⚡ beats before writing any count
  - 🔄 Normal beats = 1 image each (no split plan needed, just note "1 image")
  - 🫁 Breathing beats = 1 image each (no split plan needed, just note "1 image")

